Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.01,0:00:15.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is the first meeting of the\NCouncil of 101 in ten years.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.72,0:00:19.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Members of the Council.\NWhy have you brought us here?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.89,0:00:21.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You know very well why.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.89,0:00:24.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is about your country's\Ninvasion of JIOR.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.81,0:00:29.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I believed that the Council's rule was to\Nnot get involved in inter-human conflicts.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.90,0:00:33.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That weapon...\N"Valvrave," it was called?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.70,0:00:37.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Our own investigation has\Nconfirmed a level 3 event.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.87,0:00:40.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You disobeyed the Magius?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.95,0:00:43.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We know everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.37,0:00:48.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You violated what is the exclusive domain\Nof the Magius and kept it from us.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.38,0:00:51.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We... were careless and did not realize
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.43,0:00:54.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,that it was related to the Magius.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.26,0:00:57.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We simply intended for it\Nto be a military threat.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.18,0:00:59.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Cain Dressel.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.97,0:01:03.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He was your right-hand man in the recent revolution
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.66,0:01:06.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and has commanded an enforcement unit.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.56,0:01:07.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't believe it...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.86,0:01:11.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He is a Magius.\NFor ten years now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.61,0:01:14.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And now... you will be one, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.37,0:01:29.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Cast off the old flesh\Nand take on the new.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.96,0:01:34.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Cast off the old flesh\Nand take on the new...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.09,0:01:35.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.92,0:02:57.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now you've made me angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.84,0:03:34.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.51,0:03:40.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Unit 6? Who's piloting it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.47,0:03:43.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, Shoko-chan.\NI'll wrap this up in no time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.97,0:03:48.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Another new model?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.27,0:03:50.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It won't help them!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.77,0:03:51.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.29,0:04:11.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'll be! You've got something\Nthat lets you cheat!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.13,0:04:23.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The Captain stole it, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.59,0:04:25.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A-drei! We're getting out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.85,0:04:27.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What about the Ideal's escape pod?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.72,0:04:30.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We can't use it!\NThe engine was destroyed!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.37,0:04:55.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,JIORans!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.05,0:05:04.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Haruto!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.11,0:05:21.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Pino! Pino!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.28,0:05:23.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Big Brother! Big Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.15,0:05:27.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Just as I thought.\NThis is the original pair?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.20,0:05:30.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's no use! The controls\Naren't responding!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.91,0:05:32.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's this engine?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.13,0:05:42.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Big Brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.97,0:05:45.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Big Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.22,0:05:53.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The power is too high? Plu!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.02,0:05:58.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It won't do to become shipwrecked\Non our maiden voyage.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.06,0:06:00.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kriemhild! Do you read me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.40,0:06:03.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Prepare for fighting retreat!\NPrepare for fighting retreat!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.19,0:06:06.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We will fall back while providing\Ncover for the Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.50,0:06:15.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This stupid gear is too heavy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.62,0:06:18.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Withdraw, Q-vier!\NI know you can hear me!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.42,0:06:20.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let me keep fighting right up\Nuntil the last minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.25,0:06:21.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Withdraw!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.49,0:06:52.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What just happened?\NWhat the hell are the Valvraves?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.95,0:06:55.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All this means is that\Nwe didn't lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.21,0:07:04.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,True Calendar year 71.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.75,0:07:08.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's been two months since Module 77\N withstood Dorssia's attacks
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.63,0:07:12.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and arrived at the neutral territory of the Moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.64,0:07:18.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They appealed to the international community,\Ndenouncing the Dorssian occupation of JIOR as unjust
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.14,0:07:22.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and proclaiming themselves to be the\Nlegitimate representatives of JIOR.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.69,0:07:27.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The world celebrated them\Nas tragic heroes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.53,0:07:31.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Haruto Tokishima became the symbol of the\Nstruggle against Dorssian oppression.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.49,0:07:36.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Saki Rukino's songs became\N bestsellers that were sung
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.27,0:07:40.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,around the world as anthems\N directed towards students.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.58,0:07:43.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They collected historic amounts\Nof material aid and funding,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.79,0:07:48.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and had finally found peace\Nfor the time being.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.92,0:07:50.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.55,0:07:53.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Given the position ARUS is in,\Nwe cannot allow it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.14,0:07:57.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why not? We're only sending out the call for
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.00,0:07:59.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,all JIORans who were stranded to come to this Module.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.23,0:08:02.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There is a risk that Dorssian spies\Nwould be mingled among them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.02,0:08:07.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,For that reason, we will continue\Nto oversee customs control.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.65,0:08:10.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,At the very least, let us bring in\Ndoctors and government officials!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.40,0:08:13.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We will provide all necessary personnel.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.69,0:08:15.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.08,0:08:17.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Up next is the management of overseas assets.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.24,0:08:19.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I assume that none of you have gotten around to it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.45,0:08:20.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, we...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.75,0:08:24.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are any of you qualified to perform an audit?\NEven real-world work experience would be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.92,0:08:26.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That isn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.00,0:08:29.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, let's move on to the next order of business.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.02,0:08:30.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you would turn to page 314...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.59,0:08:38.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Regarding the hygiene management of imported goods,\Nwe will act on your behalf in this matter, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.43,0:08:39.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is that amenable to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.19,0:08:47.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The interval between attacks\Nis getting shorter.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.11,0:08:50.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is it proportional to the amount of time spent\Nat a Valvrave's controls, as I thought?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.86,0:08:54.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The conclusion this leads me to\Nis that Runes actually exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.28,0:08:58.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Working under that assumption,\Nit would explain all the phenomena.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.33,0:09:00.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What about Unit 1's avatar?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.12,0:09:03.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Her lips are sealed.\NShe really spoke?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.79,0:09:06.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.46,0:09:08.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Haruto? Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.59,0:09:13.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Haruto! Haruto!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.34,0:09:20.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You liars! You said you'd just run some\Ntests, but he's locked up like a lab rat!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.28,0:09:21.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Stop... it...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.31,0:09:24.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I asked... them to...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.27,0:09:29.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It was Haruto Tokishima who proposed\Nconducting these human experiments.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.11,0:09:34.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's vital that we learn more about\Nthe Valvraves and Kamitsuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.07,0:09:36.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Even so, that doesn't mean\Nyou have to lock him in here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.03,0:09:40.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It was also Haruto Tokishima who asked us to lock\Nhim up so that he wouldn't attack anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.71,0:09:50.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I can't let anything like that\Nhappen again... So I...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.42,0:09:53.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Haruto...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.58,0:10:30.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,As time passes, their popularity will wane\Nand the masses will lose interest.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.63,0:10:34.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how powerful their weapons, cut their \Nsupply lines, and they'll have to surrender.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.92,0:10:39.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is that what Captain Cain said?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.39,0:10:41.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You've been in a worse\Nmood than usual lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.89,0:10:45.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Did something happen between you two\Nwhen we stole the Valvrave?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.07,0:10:59.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Look, X...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.53,0:11:04.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,At this point, you and I are\Nthe only two left of our classmates.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.25,0:11:06.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I suppose we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.33,0:11:08.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Therefore...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.33,0:11:14.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We owe everything we are\Nto Captain Cain.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.11,0:11:38.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Just because we're going to Earth\Ndoesn't mean we'll be fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.32,0:11:41.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Like L-elf said, this is\Na force reconnaissance.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.49,0:11:42.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Still...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.28,0:11:47.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,President, if you see our families,\Nplease tell them we're doing fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.04,0:11:49.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Takahi, you look wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.12,0:11:53.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,These are the uniforms that you all made\Nfor us. We'll wear them with pride.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.33,0:11:55.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't right for you to wear\Nregular school uniforms.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.59,0:11:57.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Make sure you come back\Nno matter what, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.02,0:12:12.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Madam Prime Minister.\NIt's time for the sendoff.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.02,0:12:17.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,People are friendly, but countries\N are something else entirely.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.06,0:12:18.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's not that simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.20,0:12:20.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's part of the reason for\Nthis Earthfall operation.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.65,0:12:23.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Conducting a force recon mission \Ninside JIOR demonstrates
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.76,0:12:26.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,that this country has the will\N to employ military force.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.20,0:12:29.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Pressure is needed during negotiations.\NThe operation will...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.16,0:12:31.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Your dinner?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.50,0:12:32.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Simple, the way you\Nlike it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.87,0:12:36.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Take supplements with it. They taste good,\NI'll give you that, but they're just...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.75,0:12:38.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're worried about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.17,0:12:41.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's a key government figure's duty\Nto maintain her health.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.01,0:12:45.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,After we've gone down to Earth, it will\Nbe necessary to hold Module 77 together.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.89,0:12:47.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You can count on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.26,0:12:51.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make sure that you all have\Na place to come home to.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.85,0:12:54.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's my battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.65,0:12:58.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I get it. You sold\Nthe naming rights?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.82,0:13:00.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.15,0:13:04.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If I name this thing "Beast High,"\NI get money from the company.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.24,0:13:06.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Man, you really do love money, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.24,0:13:08.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.74,0:13:11.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"The beast within you\Nwill awaken!"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.83,0:13:15.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Beast High. You know,\Nlike in the commercials.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.38,0:13:20.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Energy drink Beast High,\Nnow on sale!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.26,0:13:23.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The beast within you\Nwill awaken!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.47,0:13:28.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Never heard of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.51,0:13:31.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Really? But it was\Ntotally popular!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.56,0:13:36.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Haruto.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.90,0:13:40.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Time to leave already?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.78,0:13:43.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Do you seriously plan\Nto go in that condition?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.49,0:13:47.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be fine. I'll stay in\Nthe cockpit the whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.16,0:13:50.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Haruto!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.08,0:13:55.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's crazy... It's because I've been\Ncooped up in here for so long.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.59,0:14:05.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,See? I'm perfectly fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.56,0:14:14.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't understand why,\Nbut I could tell.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.31,0:14:21.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,After you and I...\NYou felt better, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.11,0:14:28.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If I ever have an attack,\NI want you to do the same for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.38,0:14:40.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.29,0:14:42.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Haruto!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.17,0:14:48.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We're counting on you.\NEveryone's worried about their families.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.51,0:14:50.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Have you told Haruto\Nhow you feel?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.26,0:14:53.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No. This is a bad time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.35,0:14:56.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You put your own interests\Non the back burner.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.23,0:14:59.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dad said you have to do that\Nwhen you're prime minister.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.20,0:15:08.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Saki Rukino?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.82,0:15:12.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is Haruto there with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.03,0:15:15.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, has something happened\Nto Haruto Tokushima?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.75,0:15:19.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He gave me the slip. I don't think he\Ncan get far in his condition, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.71,0:15:21.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Did something happen to Haruto?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.63,0:15:24.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The colors, they...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.30,0:15:34.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on, Professor?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.26,0:15:35.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What in the world?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.14,0:15:41.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's not moving. Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.40,0:15:44.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The Runes have been depleted?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.07,0:15:56.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If I can just... get into my\Ncockpit at the harbor...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.29,0:15:57.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Haruto Tokishima.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.12,0:16:00.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.54,0:16:04.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,During your physical the other day, I had\Na transmitter injected into your body.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.55,0:16:07.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Classic you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.76,0:16:11.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Take me to Unit 1. I can't\Nwalk straight anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.34,0:16:16.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The Valvraves have all shut down\Ncompletely. It's related to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.81,0:16:17.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They've what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.18,0:16:19.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They're out of energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.19,0:16:24.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now that you mention it, we've never\Ncharged them or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.69,0:16:28.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Despite their size, the Valvraves have\Npower that exceeds that of a warship.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.44,0:16:31.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,However, they do not run on\Nany conventional power source.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.16,0:16:34.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The Valvraves are\Npowered by Runes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.66,0:16:36.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Runes?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.91,0:16:39.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Elementary information particles\Nthat are unobservable to humanity.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.08,0:16:42.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Information's elementary building blocks.\NThat's what Runes are.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.67,0:16:47.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Just as matter is composed of atoms,\Nall information is made up of Runes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.13,0:16:50.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is just a conjecture from here on out,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.24,0:16:54.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but this includes DNA, speech,\N emotions, and memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.55,0:16:58.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The thing that contains\Nthe most Runes...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.14,0:16:59.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,is a human being.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.77,0:17:05.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't believe it...\NI attack humans too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.77,0:17:09.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I suspect that you are gathering\NRunes for the Valvraves.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.15,0:17:10.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But that means...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.74,0:17:17.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go on attacking people...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.20,0:17:19.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The pact has already\Nbeen forged.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.54,0:17:23.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're now bound by blood to the Valvraves.\NA being based on the sacrifice of human life.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.33,0:17:27.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Forget it! I don't want to hurt—
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.38,0:17:29.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.18,0:17:35.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Die, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.97,0:17:41.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kamitsuki or not, I suspect that you will die\Nif I separate your head from your body.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.68,0:17:44.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Die? Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.35,0:17:48.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I died, I wouldn't cause\Npeople any more trouble.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.69,0:17:51.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I wouldn't hurt anyone else.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.36,0:17:58.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I was gone, if there were\Nno more Kamitsuki, then...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.83,0:18:03.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.29,0:18:05.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.75,0:18:07.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.25,0:18:09.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.96,0:18:15.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,L-elf. If I die, what happens\Nto the Valvrave?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.22,0:18:18.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We choose its next pilot.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.11,0:18:21.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This country needs the military\N strength that the Valvraves provide.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.64,0:18:25.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I take back what I said.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.94,0:18:30.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The Valvrave's curse\Nis mine to bear.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.15,0:18:34.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How is this Earthfall operation gonna\Nwork if we don't got any Valvraves?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.99,0:18:38.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dorssia's got a fleet waiting for us\Noutside of the neutral zone!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.91,0:18:41.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We can't leave the Moon,\Nmuch less go to Earth!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.29,0:18:46.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Can you do it? Attack people\Nso that you can save lives?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.87,0:18:48.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Watch me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.50,0:18:51.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The attacks are withdrawal symptoms\Nresulting from Rune depletion.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.92,0:18:55.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If you ingest Runes on a regular\Nbasis, you won't attack anyone.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.26,0:19:00.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,L-elf. From now on, I'm going\Nto feed on no one but you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.72,0:19:03.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I can't hurt anyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.18,0:19:07.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We'll split it 50-50. The curse.\N The hope. Everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.48,0:19:53.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It turned on!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.20,0:20:05.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No activity again today.\NIt sure is quiet, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.74,0:20:10.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They're safe if they stay on the Moon.\NI doubt they're stupid enough to leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.42,0:20:11.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Whao?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.25,0:20:14.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Physical object detected leaving\NModule 77 at high speed!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.42,0:20:21.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Valvraves, five!\NSazanami-class vessel, one!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.63,0:20:25.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We cross the neutral line in 60 seconds.\NBeyond that lies a battlefield.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.35,0:20:30.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We're about to cross the line!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.94,0:20:32.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's the Dorssian navy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.27,0:20:35.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Unit 1, you take point. Units 3, 4,\Nand 6, deploy at uniform velocity.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.36,0:20:37.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Unit 5, your mission\Nis defending this craft.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.03,0:20:41.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.79,0:20:45.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We'll go to Earth and\N meet with other JIORans.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.37,0:20:48.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,With the people who built\Nthe Valvraves, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.91,0:20:50.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And I'll ask them.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.91,0:20:53.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How to go back to being\Nhuman from a Kamitsuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.25,0:20:55.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We've crossed the line!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.54,0:21:40.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,As soon as we've taken back JIOR\Nand all this is over,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.34,0:21:44.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll destroy all the Valvraves!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.55,0:21:49.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to make it so that\Nthis curse ends with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.42,0:23:42.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a long time, Mirko.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.54,0:23:45.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't the Council of 101.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.55,0:23:53.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I am now the 68th Chancellor\Nof Dorssia, Amadeus.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.22,0:23:57.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Stay in character\Nin front of the humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.10,0:23:59.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,More importantly...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.98,0:24:00.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Those are...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.65,0:24:02.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.58,0:24:05.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The children of the Valvraves.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.58,0:24:18.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Next time, episode 14, "Hard Reentry."
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.91,0:24:24.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Valvrave the Liberator... The system\Nthat will expose the truth of the world.